TestNG - unit testing framework (Test New Generation)
also known as TDD - Test Driven Development framework
Also known as Java unit testing framework.

Purpose-  Used for writing automation test cases with Selenium in a systematuc way and generates HTML reports

Uses:
-Gives different annotations.
-Can set the priorities/sequence of the testcase execution.
-Define different dependencies.
--Can group test cases.
-has data provide feature.


Features:
It is an open source framework.
Available in the form of jar file.
Each language has there seperate testing framework.


Install testNG in Eclipse 